{"tid":745102,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[無記性]善忘嘅人可能較聰明？","createTime":"2018-07-16T12:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T13:08:18.000Z","uid":67551,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"663d1dfbae35a2e3fb5e281cc964bf6b55c9a277","tid":745102,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T12:47:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://curiousmindmagazine.com/scientists-say-that-being-forgetful-is-actually-a-sign-of-higher-intelligence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcuriousmindmagazine.com%2Fscientists-say-that-being-forgetful-is-actually-a-sign-of-higher-intelligence%2F&d=qqEyEHjbM5O92X0SLE5yGkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=7d2f5584\" target=\"_blank\">https://curiousmindmagazine.com/scientists-say-that-being-forgetful-is-actually-a-sign-of-higher-intelligence/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.maxim.com/.amp/news/forget-things-smarter-science-2017-6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.maxim.com%2F.amp%2Fnews%2Fforget-things-smarter-science-2017-6&d=qqEyEHjbM5O92X0SLE5yGkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=5460fe5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.maxim.com/.amp/news/forget-things-smarter-science-2017-6</a><br />\n<br />\n首先，我開post唔係想話自己好醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相反我係嚟救助的<br />\n<br />\n文中主旨係聰明嘅腦係會篩走（忘記）啲無用資訊，去記住同學習有用資訊<br />\n<br />\n但問題係，咩為之有用或者重要資訊？<br />\n個準則係咩？<br />\n<br />\n我好冇記性，尋日食過乜又唔記得; 溫professional exam完全唔入腦; 老細問我上個月隻job啲嘢我又完全唔記得細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢一定心諗 &quot;隻job唔係你做㗎咩，點解我記得仲清楚過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &quot;<br />\n<br />\n無論我係蠢定叻都好，我想知點可以利用/adjust個記憶準則，令個腦記得生活上人哋expect我記得嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為目前真係好唔方便，人哋溫書事半功倍，被老細Q又答到問題，我就好似智障咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而我記得好多瑣碎事，例如舊同學電話、某啲人講過或做過嘅嘢，甚至佢哋自己都唔記得、學生時代冇其他人會記住嘅碎片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無人都係咁？有無解決方法？<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc60f665b39ebcd1e8160cbfce75b4621e41857","tid":745102,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"[qoute]無論我係蠢定叻都好，我想知點可以利用/adjust個記憶準則，令個腦記得生活上人哋expect我記得嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為目前真係好唔方便，人哋溫書事半功倍，被老細Q又答到問題，我就好似智障咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">反而我記得好多瑣碎事，例如舊同學電話、某啲人講過或做過嘅嘢，甚至佢哋自己都唔記得、學生時代冇其他人會記住嘅碎片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無人都係咁？有無解決方法？<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/qoute]<br />\n屌我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對記數字尤其敏感<br />\n好多人嘅電話都背到<br />\n自己信用咭嘅資料同安全碼等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd35138435f6721758d4c13fdb2b82c1caed686","tid":745102,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T12:53:04.000Z","msg":"屌打錯個quote<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb94e7e38fd08a371825f1027cb9d91b2370a7d8","tid":745102,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dc60f665b39ebcd1e8160cbfce75b4621e41857","tid":745102,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"[qoute]無論我係蠢定叻都好，我想知點可以利用/adjust個記憶準則，令個腦記得生活上人哋expect我記得嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為目前真係好唔方便，人哋溫書事半功倍，被老細Q又答到問題，我就好似智障咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">反而我記得好多瑣碎事，例如舊同學電話、某啲人講過或做過嘅嘢，甚至佢哋自己都唔記得、學生時代冇其他人會記住嘅碎片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />